name: 11 x 14" 100% recycled 300gsm stock Print - "Gull Sea"
description:
"Gull Sea" was originally drawn using ink and graphite pencil, and once printed individually hand coloured with water colour paints.

This illustration is for anyone who can relate to being overtaken by seagulls at the beach if food is nearby. This dilemma occurs not only with seagulls at the beach, but in any situation where your enjoyment is disrupted! It can also be seen as a metaphor for interruptions in a relationship.

This limited edition print is on quality 100% recycled 300gsm Stock, individually numbered and signed, and painted with Schmincke watercolour paint. The print pictured is what you will receive, but if you prefer different colour, I can paint one for you.

The print has been size to fit into a standard 11 x 14" (280mm x 360mm) frame, and will be posted in a sturdy tube along with a free 2013 bird calendar.

name: 11 x 14" 100% recycled 300gsm stock Print - "Capture Your Thoughts"
description:
"Capture your Thoughts" was originally drawn using ink and graphite pencil, and once printed individually hand coloured with water colour paints.

This illustration is about how difficult it seems to keep track of your thoughts... being able to be aware of the thoughts you create is imperative to finding contentment. Hopefully it demonstrates that it may seem impossible, but it can be done!

This limited edition print is on quality 100% recycled 300gsm Stock, individually numbered and signed, and painted with Schmincke watercolour paint. The print pictured is what you will receive, but if you prefer different colour, I can paint one for you.

The print has been size to fit into a standard 11 x 14" (280mm x 360mm) frame, and will be posted in a sturdy tube along with a free 2013 bird calendar.

name: 11 x 14" 100% recycled 300gsm stock Print - "Let me have my Imagination"
description:
"Let me have my Imagination" was originally drawn using ink and graphite pencil, and once printed individually hand coloured with water colour paints.

This drawing makes me think about how adults try to control they way children think because they are in a position of authority. I didn’t agree with this as a child, and still don’t as an adult with 2 children of my own.

This limited edition print is on quality 100% recycled 300gsm Stock, individually numbered and signed, and painted with Schmincke watercolour paint. The print pictured is what you will receive, but if you prefer different colour, I can paint one for you.

The print has been size to fit into a standard 11 x 14" (280mm x 360mm) frame, and will be posted in a sturdy tube along with a free 2013 bird calendar.

name: Bicycle
description:
This drawing "bicycle" was originally drawn using ink pens and watercolour paint on watercolour paper.

It is printed on Arches 300GSM smooth 100% cotton paper, using photo quality ink.

Prints are available in 2 sizes (A5 & A4), please contact me if you would like a customised size.

Your print will be signed and dated, and is in a limited edition of 100. It comes protected in plastic and posted to you in a sturdy cardboard envelope.

name: 2013 Calendar - A3 poster birds
description:
(more photos to follow)
This calendar is a full colour a3 sized poster printed on 170gsm silk card.
Size : 11.7" x 16.5" (297mm x 420mm)

I chose my favourite birds from the bird a day project on my blog and flickr gallery to make this fun colourful calendar.

Printed on a3 sized card, each month features a different bird surrounded by colourful patterns and handwritten dates.

A perfect gift - even for yourself, this calendar will keep you smiling all year round!

Your calendar will be shipped to you in a sturdy cardboard roll.

name: 2013 Calendar Black and White
description:
(better photos to follow)
This calendar is a wall calendar printed on quality 170gsm silk card and provided with a clip to hang it up on your wall.
Size : 4.1" x 11.7" (105mm x 297mm)

I chose pieces of my favourite black and white illustrations to make this stylish calendar.

Printed on card, each month features a different black and white design with handwritten dates and place to list your plans for the month.

The calendar also comes with a clip to keep all the months together and to hang on your wall, and has been designed so that the image at the top can be cut off at the end of the month and used for whatever you want!

name: Where - Limited Edition Print
description:
Paper Size: 235mm x 175mm
Image Size: approx 205mm x 140mm
(watermark not on print)

The title of this painting is taken from some words appearing in the sheet music this was painted on. The girl looks lost - but I think it is more that she has lost herself in amongst what she has dressed herself in and the image she has portrayed to the world.

This printed version of the painting "where" was originally painted on old sheet music mounted onto board and done using acrylic paint and ink.

It is printed on Artist Spectrum 210GSM smooth acid free paper, using photo quality ink.

Your print will be signed and dated, and is in a limited edition of 100. It comes protected in plastic and posted to you in a sturdy cardboard envelope.
